cast.original_title: Good Luck to You, Leo Grande
cast.overview: Nancy Stokes, a retired schoolteacher, is pretty sure she has never had good sex. Now that her husband has died, she is determined to take a tour of sexual vistas that until now she has only imagined. She even has a plan; it involves an anonymous hotel room, and a sex worker who calls himself Leo Grande.
cast.title: Good Luck to You, Leo Grande

details.biography: Daryl McCormack (born January 22, 1993) is an Irish actor. He has appeared in the RTÉ One soap opera Fair City (2015–2016), the BBC series Peaky Blinders (2019–2022), and the Apple TV+ series Bad Sisters (2022). His films include Pixie (2019) and Good Luck to You, Leo Grande (2022).
